<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Portfolio — Business Operations & Cross-Functional Alignment</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0d1b35;
    --navy-mid: #162c56;
    --gold: #d4893a;
    --gold-light: #e8a85e;
    --gold-pale: #f7e8d4;
    --white: #fdf9f4;
    --off: #f5ede0;
    --gray: #6e6560;
    --text: #1e1a16;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--text);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── LANG TOGGLE ── */
  .lang-bar {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    background: rgba(13,27,53,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }

  .lang-btn {
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid rgba(212,137,58,0.5);
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    padding: 6px 18px;
    cursor: pointer;
    border-radius: 1px;
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }
  .lang-btn:hover, .lang-btn.active {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy);
    border-color: var(--gold);
  }
  .lang-btn + .lang-btn { margin-left: 8px; }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: var(--navy);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 120px 8% 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 90% 50%, rgba(212,137,58,0.13) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 10% 80%, rgba(22,44,86,0.6) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards 0.3s;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 88px);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    max-width: 780px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards 0.5s;
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.6vw, 18px);
    color: rgba(250,248,244,0.65);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 560px;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards 0.7s;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 48px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards 0.9s;
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(250,248,244,0.45);
  }

  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 32px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: rgba(200,164,90,0.5);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards 1.2s;
  }

  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), transparent);
    animation: scrollDown 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes scrollDown {
    0%, 100% { transform: scaleY(1); opacity: 0.5; }
    50% { transform: scaleY(1.3); opacity: 1; }
  }

  /* ── SECTION BASE ── */
  .section {
    padding: 100px 8%;
  }

  .section-inner {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 50px);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  /* ── EXPERTISE CARDS ── */
  .expertise-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    background: #e8d8c8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .expertise-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .exp-card {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 44px 40px;
    transition: background 0.3s;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .exp-card:hover { background: var(--off); }

  .exp-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 56px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold-pale);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
  }

  .exp-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .exp-body {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--gray);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .exp-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .tag {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(212,137,58,0.45);
    color: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  /* ── APPROACH (dark) ── */
  .approach-section {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 100px 8%;
  }

  .approach-section .section-title { color: var(--white); }

  .approach-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .approach-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  }

  .approach-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 2;
    color: rgba(250,248,244,0.75);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .approach-text strong {
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .pillars {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .pillars li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .pillar-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 28px;
  }

  .pillar-text {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(250,248,244,0.8);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .strength-panel {
    background: rgba(212,137,58,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212,137,58,0.25);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 0 2px 2px 0;
  }

  .strength-panel h3 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .strength-panel p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(250,248,244,0.75);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ── SCOPE ── */
  .scope-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .scope-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .scope-card {
    padding: 40px 36px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .scope-card.yes {
    background: #f0f6f0;
    border-top: 3px solid #4a9466;
  }

  .scope-card.no {
    background: #faf2ee;
    border-top: 3px solid #c05838;
  }

  .scope-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .scope-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .scope-card li {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #444;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .scope-card.yes li::before {
    content: '✓';
    color: #4a9466;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .scope-card.no li::before {
    content: '✕';
    color: #c05838;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── ABOUT ME ── */
  .about-section {
    padding: 100px 8%;
    background: var(--off);
  }

  .about-grid {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  }

  .about-photo {
    position: relative;
  }

  .photo-frame {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    background: #ddd5c8;
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .photo-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .photo-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    color: #a09080;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .photo-placeholder svg {
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .photo-accent {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -12px;
    right: -12px;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.3;
    border-radius: 2px;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .about-text .eyebrow { margin-bottom: 12px; }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--navy);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .about-text h2 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .about-bio {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--gray);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .about-bio strong {
    color: var(--navy);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .meta-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .meta-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }


  .contact-section {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 100px 8%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-inner {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .contact-section .eyebrow { color: var(--gold-light); }

  .contact-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .contact-section p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(250,248,244,0.65);
    line-height: 1.9;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .btn-gold {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 18px 56px;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 1px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .btn-gold:hover {
    background: var(--gold-light);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(212,137,58,0.28);
  }

  /* ── READ MORE ── */
  .read-more-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    transition: gap 0.2s;
  }
  .read-more-btn:hover { gap: 10px; }
  .read-more-btn .arrow { transition: transform 0.3s; }
  .read-more-btn.open .arrow { transform: rotate(90deg); }

  .case-detail {
    display: none;
    margin-top: 24px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(212,137,58,0.2);
  }
  .case-detail.open { display: block; }

  .case-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
    gap: 8px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .case-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .case-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    padding-top: 2px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .case-value {
    color: var(--gray);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .case-result {
    color: var(--navy);
    font-weight: 500;
  }


  .fi {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(28px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
  }
  .fi.on { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  .fi-d1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
  .fi-d2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
  .fi-d3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
  .fi-d4 { transition-delay: 0.4s; }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
  }

  /* ── LANG HIDE ── */
  .ja { display: none; }
  body.lang-ja .en { display: none; }
  body.lang-ja .ja { display: revert; }
</style>
</head>
<body class="lang-en">

<!-- LANG BAR -->
<div class="lang-bar">
  <button class="lang-btn active" onclick="setLang('en')" id="btn-en">EN</button>
  <button class="lang-btn" onclick="setLang('ja')" id="btn-ja">日本語</button>
</div>

<!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
<section class="hero">
  <p class="hero-eyebrow en">Business Operations & Cross-Functional Alignment</p>
  <p class="hero-eyebrow ja">ビジネスオペレーション & 組織横断的連携</p>

  <h1 class="en">
    Connecting People,<br>
    <em>Systems,</em> and<br>
    Outcomes.
  </h1>
  <h1 class="ja">
    人と仕組みをつなぎ、<br>
    <em>成果</em>を生み出す。
  </h1>

  <p class="hero-desc en">
    I bridge gaps between teams, build operating systems that scale,
    and turn market insight into revenue. Based between San Diego and Japan.
  </p>
  <p class="hero-desc ja">
    チーム間のズレを解消し、スケールする仕組みを構築し、<br>
    市場の洞察を売上に変える。サンディエゴと日本を拠点に活動。
  </p>

  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">20–30%</span>
      <span class="stat-label en">YoY Revenue Growth</span>
      <span class="stat-label ja">年間売上成長率</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">1/10</span>
      <span class="stat-label en">Ops Time Reduction</span>
      <span class="stat-label ja">業務時間削減率</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">5×</span>
      <span class="stat-label en">Membership Growth</span>
      <span class="stat-label ja">会員数成長率</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">30+</span>
      <span class="stat-label en">Clients (Ads)</span>
      <span class="stat-label ja">広告運用クライアント数</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="scroll-hint">
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    <span class="en">scroll</span>
    <span class="ja">スクロール</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══ EXPERTISE ═══ -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <span class="eyebrow fi en">Areas of Expertise</span>
    <span class="eyebrow fi ja">専門領域</span>
    <h2 class="section-title fi en">What I Do</h2>
    <h2 class="section-title fi ja">できること</h2>

    <div class="expertise-grid">

      <!-- 1 -->
      <div class="exp-card fi fi-d1">
        <span class="exp-num">01</span>
        <h3 class="exp-title en">Operations & Process Design</h3>
        <h3 class="exp-title ja">オペレーション改善</h3>
        <p class="exp-body en">
          Most inefficiencies aren't complex — they're misalignments.
          I identify friction between teams (Sales × Finance, Sales × Marketing, Sales × Dev),
          document the gaps, and build shared processes that stick.
          Result: 5–10 hrs/month of manual work reduced to 1/10.
        </p>
        <p class="exp-body ja">
          非効率の多くは複雑な問題ではなく、単純な「ボタンの掛け違い」です。
          営業×経理、営業×マーケ、営業×開発など部門間の摩擦を特定し、
          ドキュメント化と標準化で解消。毎月5〜10時間かかっていた作業を1/10に削減。
        </p>
        <div class="exp-tags">
          <span class="tag">Process Mapping</span>
          <span class="tag">Documentation</span>
          <span class="tag">Cross-dept Alignment</span>
        </div>
        <button class="read-more-btn" onclick="toggleCase(this)"><span class="en">Case Study</span><span class="ja">事例を見る</span> <span class="arrow">›</span></button>
        <div class="case-detail en">
          <div class="case-row"><span class="case-label">Challenge</span><span class="case-value">Email-based communication caused information gaps and repeated back-and-forth between sales and support.</span></div>
          <div class="case-row"><span class="case-label">Action</span><span class="case-value">Templated intake forms for required information. Standardized communication formats across teams.</span></div>
          <div class="case-row"><span class="case-label">Result</span><span class="case-result">Saved 30+ min per project. Reduced burden on both sides. Faster response times overall.</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="case-detail ja">
          <div class="case-row"><span class="case-label">課題</span><span class="case-value">メールベースのやり取りで情報の抜け漏れや確認の往復が多く非効率な状態。</span></div>
          <div class="case-row"><span class="case-label">施策</span><span class="case-value">必要情報のヒアリング項目をテンプレート化。コミュニケーションのフォーマットを統一。</span></div>
          <div class="case-row"><span class="case-label">結果</span><span class="case-result">1案件あたり30分以上の工数削減。営業・サポート双方の負担軽減。対応スピード向上。</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2 -->
      <div class="exp-card fi fi-d2">
        <span class="exp-num">02</span>
        <h3 class="exp-title en">Business Development</h3>
        <h3 class="exp-title ja">事業開発</h3>
        <p class="exp-body en">
          I turn unmet client needs into scalable service lines.
          Built Social Media Management (8 clients yr 1), Google Ads (30 clients in 3 yrs),
          and packaged web production to cut estimation time by 75% while streamlining
          the entire sales-to-delivery pipeline.
        </p>
        <p class="exp-body ja">
          顧客ニーズをサービス化。SNS運用（初年度8社）、Google広告運用（3年で30社）を立ち上げ。
          個別見積もりだったWeb制作をパッケージ化し、見積もり時間を1/4に短縮。
          営業からPM・開発まで一貫したフローを確立。
        </p>
        <div class="exp-tags">
          <span class="tag">Service Design</span>
          <span class="tag">Biz Dev</span>
          <span class="tag">Packaging</span>
        </div>
